Printable output (as in 'printer') should be independent of your window
contents. Unless you want to implement a PrintScreen function ;-)

<QUOTE PREVIOUSPOST="
&gt; Either display could be manually sized but the overall content would be
&gt; more comprehensive in the 'other' display.
